  "page": "Grey Worm",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\"><img alt=\"Unsullied.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/Unsullied.svg/50px-Unsullied.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/Unsullied.svg/75px-Unsullied.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b7/Unsullied.svg/100px-Unsullied.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Grey Worm</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\"><img alt=\"Unsullied.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/Unsullied.svg/50px-Unsullied.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b7/Unsullied.svg/75px-Unsullied.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b7/Unsullied.svg/100px-Unsullied.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Grey_Worm_by_Ryan_Valle-FFG.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Grey Worm by Ryan Valle-FFG.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/Grey_Worm_by_Ryan_Valle-FFG.jpg/350px-Grey_Worm_by_Ryan_Valle-FFG.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"321\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/Grey_Worm_by_Ryan_Valle-FFG.jpg/525px-Grey_Worm_by_Ryan_Valle-FFG.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3b/Grey_Worm_by_Ryan_Valle-FFG.jpg/700px-Grey_Worm_by_Ryan_Valle-FFG.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Grey Worm by Ryan Valle - FFG©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nCommander of the <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafgrey_worm.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafgrey_worm.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/List_of_actors_of_the_televised_series\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"List of actors of the televised series\">Jacob Anderson</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <br /><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_3\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 3\">Season 3</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_4\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 4\">4</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_5\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 5\">5</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_6\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 6\">6</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_7\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 7\">7</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_8\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 8\">8</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Grey Worm</b> is an <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> purchased by and sworn to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>. He is the commander of Daenerys's Unsullied and one of her trusted advisors.\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, Grey Worm is portrayed by Jacob Anderson.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Grey_Worm\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Grey Worm</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_Worm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Grey_Worm\" title=\"Category:Images of Grey Worm\">Images of Grey Worm</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>According to a semi-canon source, Grey Worm has absolutely no facial hair, though the hair atop his head is short and brown. He is stocky, of medium height and square. He has a serious looking face, on the edge of solemn. The Unsullied do not display much emotion. He is young, in his late twenties or so.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_Worm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_Worm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Grey Worm is chosen by his fellow Unsullied as the most able among them to become an officer. He is placed under the tutelage of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> to learn how to command. When <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> abolishes the Unsullied tradition of being given new names every day, Grey Worm chooses to keep the Unsullied name he had when he was freed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Grey Worm is among those present during planning for the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Meereen\" title=\"Siege of Meereen\">siege of Meereen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Daario_Naharis\" title=\"Daario Naharis\">Daario Naharis</a> states that the Unsullied could take down the gates with axes since they consider boiling oil to be no more than a warm bath. Grey Worm responds that this is false; although Unsullied would not feel burns like men do, but the oil, would blind and kill, but give the Unsullied a ram they would batter down the gate or die. Daenerys tells Grey Worm she will not throw away Unsullied lives. Later there is a plan presented to invade the city through the sewers; Daenerys includes the Unsullied as those she does not believe are appropriate for invading through the sewers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_Worm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Daenerys has Grey Worm order her <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> to travel in pairs when the <a href=\"/index.php/Sons_of_the_Harpy\" title=\"Sons of the Harpy\">Sons of the Harpy</a> begin killing her soldiers. When Daenerys disappears on <a href=\"/index.php/Drogon\" title=\"Drogon\">Drogon</a>'s back, <a href=\"/index.php/Hizdahr_zo_Loraq\" title=\"Hizdahr zo Loraq\">Hizdahr zo Loraq</a> attempts to order the Unsullied but Grey Worm and his men refuse to obey him. However when Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> goes to Grey Worm for his help in seizing control of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>, Grey Worm agrees to aid Selmy.  Grey Worm becomes a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ruling_council_of_Meereen\" title=\"Ruling council of Meereen\">ruling council of Meereen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_Worm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It is a lucky name. The name this one was born to was accursed. That was the name he had when he was taken for a slave. But Grey Worm is the name this one drew the day Daenerys Stormborn set him free.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Grey Worm to Daenerys Targaryen</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Grey_Worm\">Quotes about Grey Worm</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_Worm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Grey Worm\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I have no plans for Grey Worm's race or personal history to become important at this time, though I do reserve the right to change my mind. Sometimes the muse plays strange tricks on me.<sup id=\"cite_ref-SSM_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-SSM-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Grey_Worm&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafgrey_worm.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafgrey_worm.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Grey Worm.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-SSM-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-SSM_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-SSM_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">So Spake Martin: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/Concerning_Grey_Worm\">Concerning Grey Worm</a> (July 31, 2003)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos57.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_57\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 57\">Chapter 57</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404071024\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.142 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.771 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 865/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10754/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10294/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2069/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2284/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.310/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.6 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  745.286      1 -total\n 97.95%  729.993      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 97.69%  728.040      1 Template:Infobox\n  7.87%   58.628     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.69%   27.502      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.80%   20.882      4 Temp